an> <span class="hps">the traditional</span> <span class="hps">way of operating</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">setting up a method</span> <span class="hps">of work,</span> <span class="hps">so in</span> <span class="hps">Companex</span> <span class="hps">currently have</span> <span class="hps">the most modern</span> <span class="hps">technological tools</span> <span class="hps">created for</span> <span class="hps">sales</span> <span class="hps">and related</span> <span class="hps">area</span> <span class="hps">(such as</span> <span class="hps">smartphones,</span> <span class="hps">portable printers</span><span>, systems</span> <span class="hps">GIS,</span> <span class="hps">etc</span><span>), all</span> <span class="hps">central</span> <span class="hps">to</span> <span class="hps">an efficient</span> <span class="hps">information system that</span> <span class="hps">operates with</span> <span class="hps">the best managers</span> <span class="hps">of</span> <span class="hps atn">databases (</span><span>Oracle</span> <span class="hps">and SQL</span> <span class="hps">Server),</span> <span class="hps">which returns</span> <span class="hps">accurate data</span> <span class="hps">to make better</span> <span class="hps atn">decisions (</span><span>BI Business</span> <span class="hps">Intelligence</span> <span class="hps">system</span><span>).</span></span></p>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
