(23, 5, 0, 'DISTRIBUCION', 'DISTRIBUTION', 'DISTRIBUCION', 'DISTRIBUTION', '<div id="dis_pag">\r\n<h2 class="dis_titulo_1_bo">LOGISTICA</h2>\r\n<div class="dis_parrafo_bo">\r\n<p>Companex llega actualmente a m&aacute;s del 98% de clientes, la mayor&iacute;a mayoristas y m&aacute;s del 82% de clientes minoristas, y m&aacute;s del 92% de supermercados en todo el pa&iacute;s, recientemente tambi&eacute;n incorporamos a los vendedores Pre-ventistas.<br />Nuestra estructura comercial est&aacute; conformada por una organizaci&oacute;n enfocada en los canales de distribuci&oacute;n, los cuales son:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Mayoristas</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Supermercados</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Minoristas</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Pre-ventistas</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Otros canales alternos</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Todos ellos soportados por un equipo completo de mercadeo y trade marketing.</p>\r\n<div><img class="dis_img_bo" src="/upload/estatico/dis_img3.jpg" alt="" width="132" height="89" align="left" />Asimismo contamos con una innovadora pol&iacute;tica de precios vigentes en todo el territorio nacional,que nos permite el manejo uniforme para todos los productos distribuidos y comercializados por la empresa. Frente a la tradicional pr&aacute;ctica de trasladar mec&aacute;nicamente al cliente costos de transporte y manipuleo<br />Companex ha venido trabajando en mejorar, tanto la cadena log&iacute;stica con sus socios comerciales,como la red de producci&oacute;n. La respuesta eficiente al consumidor (ECR) permite a la cadena de distribuci&oacute;n, cumplir r&aacute;pida y oportunamente con las exigencias del cliente, mejorando as&iacute; el servicio<br /><br /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class="dis_titulo_1_bo">ALMACENES</h2>\r\n<div class="dis_parrafo_bo">\r\n<div><img class="dis_img_bo" src="/upload/estatico/dis_img5.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="105" align="left" />Los almacenes de COMPANEX BOLIVIA ocupan casi siete mil quinientos metros cuadrados provistos de la m&aacute;s moderna y &oacute;ptima&nbsp; infraestructura para garantizar el almacenamiento de cada una de las mercader&iacute;as.<br />Contamos con seis almacenes a nivel nacional en la red troncal: El Alto (Almac&eacute;n central)La Paz, Cochabamba, Santa Cruz y Oruro. En el sur del pa&iacute;s estamos en Tarija que permite abastecer a las ciudades de Yacuiba, Villaz&oacute;n y Bermejo.<br /><br /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div id="dis_pag">\r\n<h2 class="dis_titulo_1_bo">LOGISTIC</h2>\r\n<div class="dis_parrafo_bo">\r\n<p><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps">Companex</span> <span class="hps">currently reaches</span> <span class="hps">over 98</span><span>% of</span> <span class="hps">clients, most</span> <span class="hps">wholesalers and</span> <span class="hps">more than 82</span><span>% of</span> <span class="hps">retail customers,</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">over 92</span><span>% of</span> <span class="hps">supermarkets</span> <span class="hps">nationwide</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">also</span> <span class="hps">recently</span> <span class="hps">incorporated</span> <span class="hps">the sellers</span> <span class="hps atn">Pre-</span><span>Adventists</span><br /> <span class="hps">Our</span> <span class="hps">business structure</span> <span class="hps">is formed by</span> <span class="hps">an organization focused on</span> <span class="hps">distribution channels</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">which are:</span><br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span id="result_box" lang="en">&nbsp;<span class="hps">wholesalers</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span id="result_box" lang="en">&nbsp;<span class="hps">supermarkets</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span id="result_box" lang="en">&nbsp;<span class="hps">retailers</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span id="result_box" lang="en">&nbsp;<span class="hps">Pre</span><span class="atn">-</span><span>Adventists</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span id="result_box" lang="en">&nbsp;<span class="hps">Other</span> <span class="hps">alternate channels</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span id="result_box" lang="en"><br /> <span class="hps">All supported</span> <span class="hps">by</span> <span class="hps">a full team of</span> <span class="hps">marketing and</span> <span class="hps">trade marketing.</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><img class="dis_img_bo" src="/upload/estatico/dis_img3.jpg" alt="" align="left" /><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps">We also have</span> <span class="hps">an innovative</span> <span class="hps">pricing policy</span> <span class="hps">in force throughout</span> <span class="hps">the country</span><span>, which allows</span> <span class="hps">uniform</span> <span class="hps">handling</span> <span class="hps">for all</span> <span class="hps">products distributed</span> <span class="hps">and marketed</span> <span class="hps">by the company.</span> <span class="hps">Opposed to the traditional</span> <span class="hps">practice of transferring</span> <span class="hps">customer</span> <span class="hps">mechanically</span> <span class="hps">transport</span> <span class="hps">and handling</span> <span class="hps">costs</span><br /> <span class="hps">Companex</span> <span class="hps">has been working</span> <span class="hps">on improving</span> <span class="hps">both</span> <span class="hps">the supply chain</span> <span class="hps">with trading partners</span> <span class="hps">such as the</span> <span class="hps">production network.</span> <span class="hps">Efficient Consumer</span> <span class="hps">Response</span> <span class="hps">(ECR</span><span>) allows</span> <span class="hps">the distribution chain</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">fast and</span> <span class="hps">timely</span> <span class="hps">comply</span> <span class="hps">with</span> <span class="hps">customer requirements</span><span>, thus improving</span> <span class="hps">the service</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span lang="en"><span class="hps"><br /></span></span></div>\r\n<div><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps alt-edited">&nbsp;</span><span class="hps">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class="dis_titulo_1_bo">STORES</h2>\r\n<div class="dis_parrafo_bo">\r\n<div><img class="dis_img_bo" src="/upload/estatico/dis_img5.jpg" alt="" align="left" /><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps alt-edited">COMPANEX BOLIVIA</span> <span class="hps">stores</span> <span class="hps">occupy</span> <span class="hps">nearly seven thousand</span> <span class="hps">five hundred square meters</span> <span class="hps">equipped with</span> <span class="hps">the most</span> <span class="hps">modern</span> <span class="hps">infrastructure to ensure</span> <span class="hps">optimal</span> <span class="hps">storage of</span> <span class="hps">each of</span> <span class="hps">the goods.</span><br /> <span class="hps">We have six</span> <span class="hps">stores</span> <span class="hps">nationwide in</span> <span class="hps">the backbone</span><span>:</span> <span class="hps atn">El Alto (</span><span>Central warehouse</span><span>) La Paz</span><span>, Cochabamba</span><span>, Santa</span> <span class="hps">Cruz</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">Oruro.</span> <span class="hps">In the</span> <span class="hps">southern</span> <span class="hps">Tarija</span> <span class="hps">we</span> <span class="hps">can</span> <span class="hps">supply the cities</span> <span class="hps">of</span> <span class="hps">Yacuiba</span><span>, Villaz&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">Bermejo.</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
