These Games South America will have athletes in a good level?&nbsp;<br />Framework Luque&nbsp;<br />Look, we in athletics we are very hopeful i think that we have a very interesting panel athletes with great possibilities of stress in these Games South Americans.&nbsp;<br />Codesur&nbsp;<br />We can speak of some names&nbsp;<br />Framework Luque&nbsp;<br />First the marchers, framework and Paul Rodriguez, our marchers Estefany Coronado, Angela Castro, we hope the technical recovery of Claudia Balderrama and Cornejo, we also have other athletes in the background evidence that now are juveniles but arrive at its best in two years, the sprinter Bruno Rojas, our pitcher of balo Aldo Gonzales Rosemary Quispe and some other fondistas that i think can arrive with the expectation of achieving medals.\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>', '730-oliver_scheer_del_dosb_comite_olimpico_aleman_2015.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-06-07 11:43:39', '2016-07-14 06:34:45');
