(95, 9, 1, 2, 'codesur_junto_al_ministerio_de_deportes_gestiona_la_llegada_de_entrenadores_chinos_a_cochabamba', 'codesur_together_with_the_ministry_of_sports_manages_the_arrival_of_chinese_coaches_in_cochabamba', 'CODESUR junto al Ministerio de Deportes gestiona la llegada de entrenadores Chinos a Cochabamba', 'CODESUR together with the Ministry of sports manages the arrival of Chinese coaches in Cochabamba', '', '', '', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Las sonrisas es lo que m&aacute;s rebosa en la delegaci&oacute;n de siete entrenadores chinos, quienes estar&aacute;n durante un mes en Cochabamba, y fueron recibidos por el Director del Comit&eacute; de los XI Juegos Suramericanos Cochabamba 2018 (CODESUR), Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada, quien junto al Ministerio de Deportes y la Gobernaci&oacute;n de Cochabamba a trav&eacute;s del SEDEDE, programar&aacute;n el trabajo t&eacute;cnico de los visitantes.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">El Director de CODESUR al momento de darles la bienvenida, agradeci&oacute; a trav&eacute;s de los visitantes a la Rep&uacute;blica de China el poder contar con entrenadores de talla mundial quienes dejar&aacute;n toda su experiencia tanto en la formaci&oacute;n de deportistas como en las t&eacute;cnicas y metodolog&iacute;as de entrenamiento, &ldquo;la llegada de entrenadores que formaron atletas con medallas ol&iacute;mpicas dice mucho del apoyo del Gobierno Chino a la formaci&oacute;n de entrenadores y deportistas bolivianos, esto de cara nuestros Juegos Suramericanos&rdquo;, afirm&oacute; Zelada. Los siete entrenadores son especialistas en las disciplinas de b&aacute;dminton, boxeo, canotaje, levantamiento de pesas, tiro con arco y voleibol, los cuales durante el d&iacute;a realizaron visitas a diferentes escenarios deportivos, a fin de ver su adecuado acondicionamiento. Por su parte, Jorge Pardo, Presidente de la Federaci&oacute;n de Badminton, manifest&oacute; su satisfacci&oacute;n de contar con Lin Minj, joven entrenador de b&aacute;dminton que ya pudo formar a cuatro campeones mundiales y ol&iacute;mpicos. &ldquo;Es una satisfacci&oacute;n contar con t&eacute;cnicos chinos, y que un entrenador con tanta experiencia pueda capacitar en una disciplina que apenas cuenta con 7 meses de pr&aacute;ctica&rdquo;.</p>', '<p>Smiles is what more overflows in the delegation of seven chinese coaches, who will be standing a month in Cochabamba, and were received by the Director of the XI South American Cochabamba 2018 Games Organization Committee (CODESUR), Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada, who programmed the work technical of the visitors, together with the Ministry of Sports and the Government of Cochabamba, through the SEDEDE.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br /> The CODESUR Director, at the time of welcoming, thanked through the visitors of the Republic of China, of having world-class coaches who will leave all its experience, in the training of athletes, and, training methodologies and techniques, "the arrival of coaches who trained Olympic medals athletes, says a lot of the support of the Chinese Government to the formation of Bolivian coaches and athletes, in order to perform the South American Games", said Zelada. The seven coaches are specialists in the disciplines of badminton, boxing, canoeing, rising of weights, shot with ARC and volleyball, which during the day made visits to the different sports scenarios, in order see its proper conditioning. Jorge Pardo, President of the Badminton Federation, expressed his satisfaction of having Lin Minj, young badminton trainer which already formed four World and Olympic champions. "It is a satisfaction to have Chinese technicians, and a coach with so much experience who can provide training in a discipline that barely counts with 7 months of practice."</p>', '950-visita_china3.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-07-21 12:54:12', '2016-08-09 12:31:53'),
(96, 9, 1, 2, 'la_angostura_paso_el_examen_y_es_apta_para_entrenar_canotaje', 'the_angostura_pass_the_exam_and_is_suitable_for_train_canoeing', 'La Angostura, pasó el examen y es apta para entrenar Canotaje', 'The Angostura, pass the exam and is suitable for train canoeing', '', '', '', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>De manera previa al inicio del Programa de Entrenamiento Deportivo, elaborado por el Ministerio de Deportes en coordinaci&oacute;n con CODESUR, parte de la delegaci&oacute;n de entrenadores chinos, visit&oacute; la represa de la Angostura y ambientes de la Escuela Naval Militar ubicados en la zona de Carcaje, a fin de verificar el adecuado funcionamiento de estos espacios para el entrenamiento de la disciplina del canotaje.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span><span>Wang Xinxiang, entrenador de Canotaje, a trav&eacute;s de un int&eacute;rprete, manifest&oacute; su conformidad sobre la profundidad de las aguas de la Angostura y que son aptas para esta etapa de entrenamiento de la disciplina del Canotaje. Adicionalmente, la delegaci&oacute;n visit&oacute; las instalaciones de la Escuela Naval Militar, en la zona de Carcaje, espacio donde se emplazar&aacute; el trabajo t&eacute;cnico y de preparaci&oacute;n f&iacute;sica y que cuenta con un gimnasio completo, una piscina y espacios de recreaci&oacute;n, que a decir de Xinxiang, son completamente &oacute;ptimos para el trabajo que tiene planeado. Finalmente, el Director de la Escuela Naval Militar, CAP. NAV. DAEN Mois&eacute;s Mej&iacute;a, expres&oacute; su total predisposici&oacute;n para recibir a las delegaciones de entrenadores y deportistas, &ldquo;nuestras instalaciones est&aacute;n a su disposici&oacute;n, y m&aacute;s si se trata de formar deportistas&rdquo;, afirm&oacute; Mej&iacute;a.</span><br /></span></p>', '<p>Prior to the start of the program of sports training, developed by the Ministry of sports in coordination with CODESUR, part of the delegation of Chinese coaches, he visited the la Angostura dam and located in the area of Carcaje environments of the military Naval school, in order to verify the proper functioning of these spaces for training in the discipline of canoeing.&nbsp;<br /><br />Wang Xinxiang, canoeing coach, through an interpreter, said their agreement over the depth of the waters of la Angostura and that are suitable for this stage of training in the discipline of canoeing. Additionally, the delegation visited the facilities of the school Naval military, in it area of Carcaje, space where is will place the work technical and of preparation physical and that has with a gym full, a pool and spaces of recreation, that to tell of Xinxiang, are completely optimal for the work that has planned. Finally, the Director of the Naval military school, chap. NAV. DAEN Moises Mejia, expressed its total readiness to welcome the delegations of trainers and athletes, "our facilities are at your disposal, and more if it''s form athletes," said Mejia.  <a href="http://aka.ms/MicrosoftTranslatorAttribution"></a> Prior to the start of the program of sports training, developed by the Ministry of Sports in coordination with CODESUR, part of the delegation of coaches chinese, visited the dam of La Angostura and environments of the Naval School located in the area of Carcaje, in order to check the proper functioning of these spaces for the training of the discipline of canoeing.&nbsp;<br /><br />Wang Xinxiang, coach of canoeing, through an interpreter, expressed its agreement on the depth of the waters of the Angostura and that are suitable for this stage of training of the discipline of canoeing. Additionally, the delegation visited the installations of the Naval School, in the area of Carcaje, space where they fix the technical work and physical preparation and that account with a full gym, a swimming pool and recreational spaces, that to say of Xinxiang, are completely optimal for the work that you have planned. Finally, the Director of the Naval School, chap. NAV. Corrupting Moses Mejia, expressed its full willingness to receive delegations of coaches and athletes, "Our facilities are at your disposal, and more if it is a question of forming sportsmen," said Mej&iacute;a.     In a way before to the beginning of the Program of Sports Training, prepared by the Department of Sports in coordination with CODESUR, part of the delegation of Chinese trainers, he visited the dam of the Narrowness and ambiences of the Military Naval School located in the area of Carcaje, in order to verify the suitable functioning of these spaces for the training of the discipline of the boating.&nbsp;<br /><br />Wang Xinxiang, trainer of Boating, across an interpreter, it showed its conformity on the depth of the waters of the Narrowness and that are suitable for this stage of training of the discipline of the Boating. Additionally, the delegation visited the facilities of the Military Naval School, in the Carcaje area, spread where the technical work will be located and of training and that is provided with a finished gymnasium, a swimming pool and spaces of recreation, which, to say of Xinxiang, are completely ideal for the work that it has planned. Finally, the Director of the Military Naval School, CAP. NAV. DAEN Mois&eacute;s Mej&iacute;a, it expressed its entire predisposition to receive to the delegations of trainers and sportsmen, &ldquo;our facilities are at its disposal, and more if it is a question of forming sportsmen&rdquo;, affirmed Mej&iacute;a.</p>', '960-chino1.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-07-22 15:10:45', '2016-08-09 12:34:31'),
(97, 10, 1, 2, 'ministro_de_deportes_asegura_que_ya_cuenta_con_propuestas_para_la_villa_deportiva_suramericana', 'sports_minister_assures_that_already_has_proposals_for_the_villa_deportiva_suramericana', 'Ministro de Deportes asegura que ya cuenta con propuestas para la Villa Deportiva Suramericana', 'Sports Minister assures that already has proposals for the Villa Deportiva Suramericana', '', '', '', '', '<p><em>Una vez consolidada la transferencia de terrenos de la Tamborada</em></p>\r\n<p>Despu&eacute;s de todas las gestiones realizadas por CODESUR antes las autoridades de la Universidad Mayor de San Sim&oacute;n, y en la &uacute;ltima parte, con la Gobernaci&oacute;n de Cochabamba, el Ministro de Deportes, Tito Monta&ntilde;o, asegura que ya se cuenta con propuestas para la consolidaci&oacute;n de la Villa Deportiva Suramericana en la zona de la Tamborada.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ahora que se transfirieron los terrenos, como establece la Ley 2868, nos reuniremos el Ministerio de Deportes, el Ministerio de Obras P&uacute;blicas y CODESUR para de consensuar un cronograma de trabajo y precisar detalles, antes de ponernos manos a la obra en la construcci&oacute;n de nuestra esperada Villa Suramericana&rdquo;, afirm&oacute;&nbsp; Monta&ntilde;o.</p>\r\n<p>La proyecci&oacute;n de la Villa Deportiva Suramericana contemplar&aacute; el hospedaje, en la etapa m&aacute;s alta, a 4.388 deportistas, llegados de 13 pa&iacute;ses, para lo cual, tomando en cuenta los terrenos de las Tamborada, todav&iacute;a se definir&aacute;n la cantidad de bloques, pisos y departamentos necesarios.</p>\r\n<p>La ventaja de realizar la construcci&oacute;n de la Villa Deportiva Suramericana, a trav&eacute;s de la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda, es que se pueden realizar contrataciones directas, contempladas por ley, que hacen m&aacute;s efectivo el trabajo y en menor tiempo.</p>', '<pre><em><span>Once consolidated the transfer of land Tamborada</span></em></pre>\r\n<pre><span><pre><span>After all the efforts made by CODESUR before the authorities of the University of San Sim&oacute;n, last part, with the Governor of Cochabamba, the Minister of Sports, Tito Montano says that already has proposals for consolidation the Villa Deportiva Suramericana area Tamborada.\r\n"Now that the land was transferred, as established by Law 2868, we will meet the Ministry of Sports, the Ministry of Public Works and CODESUR for a consensus on a work schedule and precise details, before we get to work on building our expected Villa Suramericana, "Montano said.\r\nThe projection of the Villa Deportiva Suramericana will consider lodging at the highest stage, 4,388 athletes, coming from 13 countries, for which, taking into account the grounds of the Tamborada, yet the number of blocks, houses and apartments will be defined necessary.\r\nThe advantage of carrying out the construction of the Villa Deportiva Suramericana, through the State Housing Agency, is that you can make direct contracts referred by law to make it more effective work and less time.</span></pre>\r\n<br /></span></pre>', '970-min_entrev_peq.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-07-29 14:59:00', '2016-07-29 15:17:34'),
(98, 11, 1, 2, 'villa_puede_iniciar_trabajos_en_unos_dias', 'villa_can_start_work_in_a_few_days', 'Villa puede iniciar trabajos en unos días', 'Villa can start work in a few days', '', '', '', '', '<p>LT -&nbsp;Betty Rojas Rodr&iacute;guez</p>\r\n<p>Una vez encontrada la v&iacute;a legal que se requiere para autorizar a la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda y al Ministerio de Obras P&uacute;blicas, para que pueda ingresar a los terrenos de La Tamborada e iniciar con los trabajos preliminares de construcci&oacute;n de la Villa Suramericana, la ejecuci&oacute;n de las obras podr&iacute;an iniciarse la siguiente semana.</p>\r\n<p>El Comit&eacute; Organizador de los Juegos, el Ministerio de Deportes, la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda y el Ministerio de Obras P&uacute;blicas se reunieron ayer para definir los pasos legales a seguir y las obras de la Villa no presenten ning&uacute;n problema a futuro.</p>\r\n<p>"La reuni&oacute;n fue con el director de la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda a objeto de intercambiar criterios respecto a la transferencia de los terrenos de la Tamborada para la construcci&oacute;n de la Villa Suramericana, se est&aacute;n haciendo los an&aacute;lisis legales en la Gobernaci&oacute;n, para que la transferencia no tenga ning&uacute;n problema en lo posterior", dijo Tito Monta&ntilde;o, ministro de Deportes.</p>\r\n<p>El lunes pasado, la Universidad Mayor de San Sim&oacute;n (UMSS) envi&oacute; a la Gobernaci&oacute;n la minuta de transferencia de los terrenos de La Tamborada. Una vez concretado ese paso, la Gobernaci&oacute;n y el Codesur iniciaron el estudio legal para agilizar los tr&aacute;mites de la cesi&oacute;n o, en su defecto, ver las v&iacute;as legales, que permitan a la Gobernaci&oacute;n autorizar a la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda iniciar los trabajos.</p>\r\n<p>Con la parte legal finalizada, el siguiente paso ser&aacute; que la instituci&oacute;n encargada de la construcci&oacute;n de la Villa Suramericana realice el levantamiento topogr&aacute;fico de los terrenos en La Tamborada, para despu&eacute;s terminar con el proyecto a dise&ntilde;o final de la Villa.</p>\r\n<p>Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada, director de los Juegos, explic&oacute; que se determin&oacute; que la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda sea la encargada de la construcci&oacute;n de la Villa Suramericana, porque cuenta con un decreto que le permite realizar licitaciones mediante invitaci&oacute;n directa, para agilizar las obras.</p>\r\n<p>El presupuesto estimado inicial para la Villa Suramericana era de 70 millones de d&oacute;lares, para la construcci&oacute;n y el equipamiento; sin embargo, ayer Monta&ntilde;o asegur&oacute; que este estimado podr&iacute;a sufrir algunas modificaciones "en funci&oacute;n de algunos requerimientos por parte de la comisi&oacute;n de Odesur".</p>', '<p>Once you have found legal means required to authorize the State Housing Agency and the Ministry of Public Works, so you can enter the grounds of La Tamborada and start the preliminary construction work on the Villa Suramericana execution the works could begin next week.<br />The Organizing Committee of the Games, the Ministry of Sports, the State Housing Agency and the Ministry of Public Works met yesterday to define the legal steps to follow and works of the Villa not present any problem in the future.<br />"The meeting with the director of the State Housing Agency to object to exchange views regarding the transfer of land Tamborada for the construction of the Villa Suramericana, are becoming legal analysis in the Interior, so that the transfer not have any problems in the future ", said Tito Montano, Minister of Sports.<br />Last Monday, the University of San Sim&oacute;n (UMSS) sent the Government the draft of transfer of land Tamborada. Once finalized that step, the Government and the CODESUR initiated the legal study to expedite the process of the assignment or, failing that, see legal channels, to enable the Government to authorize the State Housing Agency to start work.<br />With the legal completed, the next step will be the institution responsible for the construction of the Villa Suramericana perform the topographic survey of the land in La Tamborada, then end the project final design of the Villa.<br />Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada, director of the Games, said it was determined that the State Housing Agency is responsible for the construction of the Villa Suramericana, because it has a decree that allows you to make bids by direct invitation to expedite the works.<br />Initial estimated budget for Villa Suramericana was 70 million dollars for the construction and equipment; however, Montano said yesterday that this estimate could undergo some modifications "according to some requirements by the commission Odesur".</p>', '980-dsc_0313_peq.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-07-30 06:04:09', '2016-08-09 12:33:37'),
(99, 11, 1, 2, 'angela_castro_emociona_ver_la_bandera_boliviana_en_otro_pais', 'angela_castro_excited_see_the_flag_bolivian_in_another_country', 'Angela Castro: "Emociona ver la bandera boliviana en otro país¨', 'Angela Castro: "excited see the flag Bolivian in another country"', '', '', '', '', '<p>"Es el sue&ntilde;o de todo atleta", afirm&oacute; la&nbsp;abanderada de la delegaci&oacute;n boliviana. "Es una emoci&oacute;n bien grande ver la bandera boliviana en otro pa&iacute;s. Para que todos vean que Bolivia est&aacute; presente", agreg&oacute; la atleta.</p>\r\n<p>Adem&aacute;s, prometi&oacute;: "Es un honor que me hayan elegido.&nbsp;No los vamos a defraudar".</p>\r\n<p>Entrevista---&gt;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.foxsports.com.bo/videos/735882307829-angela-castro-emociona-ver-la-bandera-boliviana-en-otro-pais">http://www.foxsports.com.bo/videos/735882307829-angela-castro-emociona-ver-la-bandera-boliviana-en-otro-pais</a></p>\r\n<p>Gentileza FOX SPORT</p>', '<p><span>"It is the dream of every athlete," said the leader of the Bolivian delegation. "It is a great emotion to see the Bolivian flag in another country. For all to see that Bolivia is present", added the athlete.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>In addition, promised: "is an honor that I have chosen. We won''t them to defraud".&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Interview---&gt;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.foxsports.com.bo/videos/735882307829-angela-castro-emociona-ver-la-bandera-boliviana-en-otro-pais">http://www.foxsports.com.bo/videos/735882307829-angela-castro-emociona-ver-la-bandera-boliviana-en-otro-pais</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span>Gentleness FOX SPORT<br /></span></p>', '990-captura_de_pantalla_20160802_a_las_4.13.42_p.m._copia.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-08-02 13:28:25', '2016-08-09 12:35:24'),
(100, 11, 1, 2, 'entrenadores_chinos_evaluan_y_ofrecen_llevar_a_mas_deportistas_a_su_pais', 'chinese_coaches_evaluate_and_offer_more_athletes_take_to_their_country', 'ENTRENADORES CHINOS EVALÚAN Y OFRECEN LLEVAR A MÁS DEPORTISTAS A SU PAÍS', 'CHINESE COACHES EVALUATE AND OFFER MORE ATHLETES TAKE TO THEIR COUNTRY', '', '', '', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">La delegaci&oacute;n de entrenadores chinos, que lleg&oacute; siguiendo el Plan Macro de Cooperaci&oacute;n con la Rep&uacute;blica Popular de China y el Ministerio de Deportes, ya identific&oacute; deportistas que podr&iacute;an acompa&ntilde;arlos de retorno a su pa&iacute;s, para dar continuidad a su entrenamiento.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Una vez instalada la delegaci&oacute;n de entrenadores chinos, desde el pasado 16 de julio, realizaron el relevamiento de los escenarios deportivos y procedieron a evaluar el nivel f&iacute;sico t&eacute;cnico de nuestros deportistas en cada una de las disciplinas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Des esa forma, en algunas disciplinas ya se identificaron deportistas que podr&iacute;an ser promocionados para ampliar su capacitaci&oacute;n t&eacute;cnica y f&iacute;sica en la Rep&uacute;blica Popular de China. &ldquo;Con la llegada de los entrenadores chinos no culmina el apoyo de la Rep&uacute;blica de China, el Plan que se tiene contempla la posibilidad de becar a nuevos deportistas para ampliar su formaci&oacute;n. Adem&aacute;s, est&aacute; contemplada un Plan de Equipamiento, logrando un apoyo integral hist&oacute;rico para nuestro pa&iacute;s&rdquo;, afirmo el Director de CODESUR, Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">ANTECEDENTES<br />A continuaci&oacute;n resumimos la experiencia de los entrenadores chinos que llegaron a Cochabamba, y que no solo cuentan con muchos a&ntilde;os de experiencia en su &aacute;rea, sino que acompa&ntilde;aron el triunfo, en muchos casos, mundial y ol&iacute;mpico, de varios de sus alumnos.</p>', '<p><span>The delegation of Chinese coaches, who arrived following the Macro Plan for cooperation with the people''s Republic of China and the Ministry of sports, already identified athletes who could accompany them back to their country, to continue their training.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>Once installed the delegation of Chinese coaches since last July 16, conducted the survey of the sporting arenas and proceeded to assess the physical-technical level of our athletes in each of the disciplines.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Des that form, in some disciplines already is identified athletes that could be promoted to extend its training technical and physical in the Republic Popular of China. "With the arrival of Chinese coaches not end the support of the Republic of China, Plan that contemplates the possibility of scholarships to new athletes to extend their training. Is also referred to a Plan of equipment, achieving a historic comprehensive support for our country", stated the Director of CODESUR, Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Background&nbsp;</span><br /><span>below summarize the experience of the Chinese coaches who came to Cochabamba, and that not only have many years of experience in his area, but it was accompanied by the triumph, in many cases, world and Olympic , several of his students.</span></p>', '1000-13725066_1746702512269243_4878312722453188570_o.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-08-02 13:49:50', '2016-08-09 12:35:53'),
(101, 11, 1, 2, 'codesur_convoca_a_alcaldes_para_evaluar_cumplimiento_de_compromisos', 'codesur_convenes_mayors_to_assess_compliance_with_commitments', 'CODESUR convoca a alcaldes para evaluar cumplimiento de compromisos', 'CODESUR convenes mayors to assess compliance with commitments', '', '', '', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">En el marco de los compromisos asumidos por los 12 alcaldes de Cochabamba, para participar como sede de los XI Juegos Suramericanos 2018, la directiva de CODESUR, convoc&oacute; a una reuni&oacute;n extraordinaria, a fin de evaluar el cumplimiento de las tareas pendientes.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&ldquo;El compromiso asumido por nuestros acaldes ha sido determinante para reafirmar a Cochabamba como la sede de nuestros Juegos Suramericanos, y ma&ntilde;ana estaremos reunidos con ellos junto a su equipo t&eacute;cnico y jur&iacute;dico, para hacer seguimiento a las tareas asumidas&rdquo;, afirm&oacute; Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada.<br />Mencionar que los municipios que ser&aacute;n sede de los XI Juego Suramericanos en los 35 deportes son: Arbieto, Cercado, &nbsp;Cliza, Colcapirhua, Punata, Quillacollo, Sacaba, Tarata, Tiquipaya, Tolata, Villa Tunari y &nbsp;Vinto.<br />Cada municipio contempla la construcci&oacute;n de escenarios deportivos, los cuales CODESUR tiene el compromiso de abastecer con todos los equipamientos deportivos, &oacute;ptimos para competencias reglamentarias de acuerdo a los organismos internacionales.</p>', '<p><span>In the framework of the commitments made by 12 mayors of Cochabamba, to participate as a venue for the Eleventh South American 2018 games, CODESUR policy, convened an extraordinary meeting, in order to assess the implementation of the pending tasks.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>"The commitment made by our acaldes has been determinant to reaffirm to Cochabamba as the headquarters of our South American Games, and tomorrow will be gathered with them along with his team of technical and legal, to track the tasks assumed", said Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>Mention that municipalities which will be the headquarters of the 11th game South American in 35 sports are: Arbieto, Cercado, Cliza, Colcapirhua, Punata, Quillacollo, Sacaba, Tarata, Tiquipaya, Tolata, Villa Tunari and Vinto.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>Each municipality includes the construction of sports arenas, which CODESUR is committed to supply with all the sports, optimal equipment for regulatory powers agree to international bodies.</span></p>', '1010-dr._sello.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-08-02 15:44:53', '2016-08-09 12:34:05');
