(102, 11, 1, 2, '12_alcaldes_rendiran_cuentas_sobre_obras', '12_mayors_accountable_on_works', '12 alcaldes rendirán cuentas sobre obras', '12 mayors accountable on works', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: xx-small;">Fuente: OPINION</span></p>\r\n<p>El Comit&eacute; Organizador de los Juegos Suramericanos&nbsp;Cochabamba&nbsp;2018 (Codesur) y los 12 alcaldes que est&aacute;n comprometidos en la materializaci&oacute;n de obras para la cita continental se ver&aacute;n las caras ma&ntilde;ana (14:30) en la Llajta para definir el grado de avance, detectar falencias y abordar el factor presupuestario con relaci&oacute;n a los escenarios que deber&aacute;n estar concluidos en dos a&ntilde;os.<br /><br />Consolidar dicho aspecto &ldquo;de una vez por todas&rdquo; es el principal objetivo. As&iacute; lo entendi&oacute; el director de Codesur, Jos&eacute; Luiz Zelada, quien dijo estar preocupado porque&nbsp;Cercado&nbsp;a&uacute;n no present&oacute; los dise&ntilde;os finales de las nueve infraestructuras de magnitud que efectuar&aacute;, entre las que figuran un patin&oacute;dromo y un complejo acu&aacute;tico.<br /><br />El Comit&eacute; les curs&oacute; la convocatoria a todas las autoridades, incluida la de Villa Tunari. Deber&aacute;n formar parte de la reuni&oacute;n los alcaldes y el personal t&eacute;cnico y jur&iacute;dico de Cliza,&nbsp;Cercado,&nbsp;Quillacollo, Arbieto, Sacaba, Tarata,&nbsp;Punata, Vinto, Colcapirhua, Tiquipaya, Tolata y, por &uacute;ltimo, Villa Tunari.<br /><br />Si bien un informe elaborado por este medio, publicado el 17 de julio pasado, detect&oacute; que solo 8 de 37 deportes cuentan con infraestructuras en condiciones para recibir los Juegos, Zelada intent&oacute; ser optimista. Destac&oacute; que el 80 por ciento de las obras encaradas por el Gobierno Central est&aacute; en ejecuci&oacute;n. Cit&oacute; como ejemplo el Coliseo Municipal del Tr&oacute;pico, que cuenta con la mitad de su avance total.<br /><br />El jefe de los Juegos de la Alcald&iacute;a de&nbsp;Cercado, Sergio Ren&aacute;n L&oacute;pez, explic&oacute; con anterioridad que el plan trazado para el inicio de trabajos es &ldquo;dosificado&rdquo;. Esto quiere decir que, por tratarse de nueve obras significativas en materia presupuestaria, varias tendr&aacute;n que ser iniciadas en la siguiente gesti&oacute;n.<br /><br />El Comit&eacute; ya inici&oacute; un operativo de seguimiento sobre coliseos montados en Vinto y Tarata, por ejemplo. En este &uacute;ltimo municipio, se ha consolidado un complejo de hipismo en la Escuela Militar de Sargentos del Ej&eacute;rcito (EMSE). Tiene casi un 78 por ciento de avance.<br /><br />VILLA M&Aacute;S CHICA Todo apunta a que la Villa Suramericana, que ser&aacute; terminada a fines de 2017 y emplazada sobre 13 hect&aacute;reas en la Tamborada, ya no contar&aacute; con 1088 departamentos en 17 torres, c&aacute;lculo que hab&iacute;a sido proyectado en febrero pasado. De momento, se prev&eacute; que tendr&aacute; 672 apartamentos divididos en 14 bloques, lo que supone 416 menos con respecto al plan inicial elaborado por el &Aacute;rea de Infraestructura del Comit&eacute; Organizador de los Juegos.<br /><br />Fueron suprimidos, de manera no definitiva, tres edificios de aquel dise&ntilde;o inicial que ha sido expuesto hace seis meses ante la Comisi&oacute;n T&eacute;cnica de Odesur, ocasi&oacute;n en la que se hizo el desglose de los m&oacute;dulos del proyecto y que tambi&eacute;n se observ&oacute; las bondades que tendr&aacute; la ciudadela (micromercado, cajeros autom&aacute;ticos, un spa y un cub&iacute;culo para disciplinas culturales, entre otros aspectos).<br /><br />Las modificaciones se dieron luego de que Zelada y la Agencia Estatal de Vivienda se reunieran recientemente para definir la funcionalidad de la Villa.<br /><br />El exasesor del Ministerio de Deportes explic&oacute; ayer que se proyecta que cada uno de los 14 bloques contar&aacute; con 12 pisos y poseer&aacute; 48 departamentos.<br /><br />&ldquo;Se hizo un c&aacute;lculo del flujo pico de atletas que llegar&aacute;n. Asciende a 4.388. Debemos tomar ese dato como referencia&rdquo;.<br /><br />CONSTRUCCI&Oacute;N EN SEPTIEMBRE Codesur mantiene el jueves 4 de este mes como fecha tentativa &ldquo;ideal&rdquo; para realizar las labores preliminares en la Tamborada. Esto es: estudios de suelo y levantamiento topogr&aacute;fico. Sin embargo, reci&eacute;n en septiembre se dar&aacute; &ldquo;luz verde&rdquo; a los trabajos de construcci&oacute;n de la ciudadela.<br /><br />La Universidad Mayor de San Sim&oacute;n ya firm&oacute; la minuta de transferencia, pero a&uacute;n restan tres elementos para que comiencen las labores: la aprobaci&oacute;n de la planimetr&iacute;a, el visto bueno del dise&ntilde;o arquitect&oacute;nico por parte de la Alcald&iacute;a y solucionar lo referente al factor ambiental.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: xx-small;">Source: OPINION&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>The Committee organizing the games South American Cochabamba 2018 (Codesur) and 12 mayors who are committed to the realization of works for the continental meeting will be tomorrow (14:30) faces in the Llajta to define the degree of advancement, detect shortcomings and address budgetary factor in relation to the scenarios that should be completed in two years.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Consolidate the appearance "once for all" is the main objective. So understood it Codesur director, Jos&eacute; Luiz Zelada, who said he was concerned because fencing still did not provide final designs of nine infrastructures of magnitude which will take place, including a skating rink and an aquatic complex.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>The Committee extended the call to all authorities, including the Villa Tunari. The mayors and the technical and legal staff of Cliza, fencing, Quillacollo, Arbieto, Sacaba, Tarata, Punata, Vinto, Colcapirhua, Tiquipaya, Tolata and, finally, Villa Tunari should form part of the meeting.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Although a report prepared by this means, published on 17 July last, found that only 8 of 37 sports have infrastructures able to receive games, Zelada tried to be optimistic. He stressed that 80 percent of the works undertaken by the Central Government is running. He cited as an example the Municipal Coliseum of the tropics, which has half of its total advance.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Chief of the games of the municipality of Cercado, Sergio Ren&aacute;n L&oacute;pez, explained earlier that the plan drawn up for the start of works is "dispensed". This means that, by being nine significant works in budgetary matters, several will have to be initiated in the following management.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span><span>The Committee already began an operation mounted in Vinto and Tarata coliseums monitoring, for example. In this latter municipality has become a complex of horse racing in the military sergeants from the Army School (EMSE). It has nearly 78 percent of advance.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>VILLA more all girl points to Villa Suramericana, which will be completed by the end of 2017 and located on 13 acres in the Tamborada, already will not count with 1088 departments in 17 towers, which had been projected last February. At the moment, is expected which will have 672 apartments divided into 14 blocks, representing 416 less with respect to the initial plan developed by the Area of infrastructure of the organizer of the Games Committee.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Were abolished, not permanently, three buildings in the initial design that has been exposed for six months before the technical Commission of Odesur, occasion in which the breakdown of the modules of the project was made and also noted the benefits that will have the Citadel (micromercado, ATMs, a spa and a cubicle for cultural disciplines, among others).&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Modifications occurred once Zelada and State housing agency recently met to define the functionality of the Villa.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>The exasesor of the Ministry of sports said yesterday that projected that each of the 14 blocks will have 12 floors and will own 48 departments.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>"Made a calculation of the flow peak of athletes who will arrive. Amounts to 4,388. We must take this fact as a reference".&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Construction in September Codesur remains tentative date "ideal" to do the preliminary work in the Tamborada Thursday 4th of this month. This is: soil and topographic studies. However, recently in September is will give "light green" to the works of construction of the Citadel.&nbsp;</span><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span><span>The Universidad Mayor de San Sim&oacute;n already signed the minutes of transfer, but still remaining three elements so that they start work: approval of the floor plan, the approval of the architectural design by the Mayor''s Office and solve regards the environmental factor</span><br /></span></p>', '1020-director.jpg', '1', 0, '2016-08-02 15:55:04', '2016-08-02 15:55:13'),
(103, 12, 1, 2, 'llega_el_dia_d_y_codesur_evalua', 'becomes_the_dday_and_codesur_evaluates', 'Llega el “Día D” y Codesur evalúa', 'Becomes the "D-day" and Codesur evaluates', '', '', '', '', '<p><span>El Comit&eacute; Organizador de los Juegos Suramericanos&nbsp;</span>Cochabamba<span>&nbsp;2018 (Codesur) se reunir&aacute; hoy con 12 alcaldes municipales para abordar aspectos relacionados con los avances en las infraestructuras que comprometieron para el encuentro continental</span><br /><br /><span>Desde las 14:30, la Sala Vip del F&eacute;lix Capriles concentrar&aacute; a las autoridades y sus equipos jur&iacute;dicos, que rendir&aacute;n sus informes ante el director de Codesur, Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada, quien inst&oacute; a cumplir con las responsabilidades asumidas</span><br /><br /><span>Se tratar&aacute; de una reuni&oacute;n en la que participar&aacute;n Vinto, Tarata,&nbsp;</span>Punata<span>,&nbsp;</span>Cercado<span>, Cliza, Colcapirhua, Tiquipaya, Tolata, Villa Tunari,&nbsp;</span>Quillacollo<span>, Arbieto y Sacaba.</span></p>\r\n<p><span><a href="http://opinion.com.bo/opinion/articulos/2016/0803/noticias.php?id=196461">http://opinion.com.bo/opinion/articulos/2016/0803/noticias.php?id=196461</a><br /></span></p>', '<p><span>The Committee organizing the games South American Cochabamba 2018 (Codesur) is meeting today with 12 municipal mayors to address aspects related to advances in infrastructure that committed to the continental meeting&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>14:30, the Vip room of the Felix Capriles focus to the authorities and their legal teams, which surrender their reports to the director of Codesur, Jos&eacute; Luis Zelada who urged to comply with the responsibilities assumed&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>will seek a meeting involving Vinto, Tarata, Punata, fencing, Cliza, Colcapirhua, Tiquipaya, Tolata, Villa Tunari, Quillacollo, Arbieto and Sacaba.</span></p>\r\n<p><span><a href="http://opinion.com.bo/opinion/articulos/2016/0803/noticias.ph