(1, 'Capacitaciòn exclusiva', 'Exclusive training', '<p>A fin de que cumplas tus tareas de la mejor manera, se te capacitara en las tareas que desarrollaras.</p>\r\n<p>Estos cursos, seminarios&nbsp; y talleres ser&aacute;n dictados por formadores certificados y preparados.</p>', '<p><span><span>In order to</span> <span>fulfill your</span> <span>tasks</span> <span>in the best way</span><span>, you are</span> <span>trained in</span> <span>the tasks that</span> <span>you will develop</span><span>.</span><br /><span>These courses</span><span>, seminars</span> <span>and workshops will be</span> <span>taught by certified</span> <span>trainers</span> <span>and</span> <span>prepared</span><span>.</span></span></p>', 1, 1),
(2, 'Amigos y contactos', 'Friends and contacts', '<p>Te ofreceremos la oportunidad de conocer personas nuevas a nivel nacional e internacional, por lo cual podr&aacute;s expandir tu agenda de contactos que te ayudaran en tu futuro.</p>', '<p><span><span>We offer you the</span> <span>opportunity to meet new</span> <span>national and international</span> <span>level</span> <span>people</span><span>, so</span> <span>you can expand</span> <span>your</span> <span>contact book</span> <span>that will help you</span> <span>in your future.</span></span></p>', 2, 1),
(3, 'Regalos unicos', 'Unique gifts', '<p>Se te obsequiaran distintos art&iacute;culos y beneficios gracias a nuestros auspiciadores oficiales.</p>', '<p><span><span>You will</span> <span>given away</span> <span>various items and</span> <span>benefits from</span> <span>our</span> <span>official</span> <span>sponsors</span><span>.</span></span></p>', 3, 1),
(4, 'Uniforme de voluntario.', 'Volunteer uniform.', '<p>Los voluntarios tendremos&nbsp; un uniforme &uacute;nico, que solo t&uacute; lo podr&aacute;s lucir.</p>', '<p><span><span>Volunteers</span> <span>will have a</span> <span>single uniform</span><span>,</span> <span>so</span> <span>that only you</span> <span>can wear</span></span></p>', 4, 1),
(5, 'Acreditación de voluntario', 'Volunteer Card', '<p>Por cuestiones de seguridad solo las personas acreditadas tienen acceso a ciertas &aacute;reas dentro de los escenarios deportivos y las villas de atletas, estar&aacute;s acreditado debidamente para que tengas los accesos necesarios y as&iacute; realizar tus tareas sin preocupaciones.<strong></strong></p>', '<p><span><span>For security reasons</span> <span>only</span> <span>accredited persons</span> <span>have access</span> <span>to certain areas</span> <span>within the</span> <span>sports venues</span> <span>and</span> <span>athletes</span> <span>villas</span><span>,</span> <span>will be</span> <span>duly accredited</span> <span>so that you have</span> <span>the necessary access</span> <span>and thus perform</span> <span>your tasks</span> <span>without worries.</span></span></p>', 5, 1),
(6, 'Refrigerio', 'Food', '<p>Se te brindara alimentaci&oacute;n de buena calidad&nbsp; y de acuerdo a tus horarios de servicio durante todo el evento.</p>', '<p><span><span>It</span> <span>gives</span> <span>you</span> <span>good quality food</span> <span>and according to</span> <span>your schedule</span> <span>service</span> <span>throughout the event</span><span>.</span></span></p>', 6, 1),
(7, 'Seguro contra accidentes', 'Accident insurance', '<p>Se te brindara un seguro contra accidentes durante el desarrollo del evento.</p>', '<p><span><span>It</span> <span>will offer you</span> <span>insurance against</span> <span>accidents during</span> <span>the event.</span></span></p>', 7, 1),
(8, 'Certificado de participación', 'Participation certificate.', '<p>Se te otorgara un certificado de participaci&oacute;n por las horas de servicio del &aacute;rea en la que participaste y los cursos de capacitaci&oacute;n, detallando las horas acad&eacute;micas que representan.</p>', '<p><span><span>You are awarded a</span> <span>certificate of participation for</span> <span>the</span> <span>hours of the</span> <span>area in which</span> <span>you participated</span> <span>and</span> <span>training courses</span><span>, detailing</span> <span>academic</span> <span>hours</span> <span>they represent.</span></span></p>', 8, 1);
