(1, 'Protocolo', 'Protocol', '<p>Los voluntarios de esta &aacute;rea se encargaran de coadyuvar la ceremonia inaugural y de&nbsp; clausura, recepci&oacute;n de atletas y premiaciones de cada una de las disciplinas que se llevaran a cabo. Por otro lado tambi&eacute;n se encargaran del izado de banderas y todos los actos solemnes que se desarrollen.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Guiar a las delegaciones&nbsp; y      ejecutivos de la Organizaci&oacute;n Deportiva Suramericana &ndash; ODESUR en su      desplazamiento en Cochabamba. .</li>\r\n<li>Apoyar en Protocolo ceremonial y protocolo      deportivo.</li>\r\n<li>Realizar servicios de traducci&oacute;n e      interpretaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>Participar en recepciones, hoteles y      aeropuertos, ayudar con las tareas de bienvenida, recreaci&oacute;n y de      interpretaci&oacute;n, responsables de actividades que van desde escoltar los      atletas y los dispensadores de medallas, las ceremonias de apertura y      cierre.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span><strong></strong></span><span><span><span>Volunteers in this</span> <span>area</span> <span>will be in charge</span> <span>of assisting</span> <span>the opening ceremony and</span> <span>closing</span> <span>reception</span> <span>and</span> <span>awards</span> <span>athletes</span> <span>from each of</span> <span>the disciplines that</span> <span>will take place</span><span>.</span> <span>On the other hand</span> <span>also</span> <span>in charge</span> <span>of</span> <span>hoisting</span> <span>flags</span> <span>and all the</span> <span>solemn ceremonies</span> <span>that take place</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Guiding</span> <span>delegations</span> <span>and executives of the</span> <span>South American Sports Organization</span> <span>-</span> <span>ODESUR</span> <span>their displacement in</span> <span>Cochabamba.</span> <span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Support</span> <span>in</span> <span>ceremonial</span> <span>protocol</span> <span>and</span> <span>protocol</span> <span>sport</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Conduct</span> <span>translation and</span> <span>interpretation.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Participate in</span> <span>receptions,</span> <span>hotels and airports,</span> <span>help with homework</span> <span>welcome</span><span>, recreation</span> <span>and</span> <span>interpretation</span><span>,</span> <span>responsible for</span> <span>activities ranging from</span> <span>escorting</span> <span>athletes and</span> <span>medals</span> <span>dispensers</span><span>,</span> <span>the</span> <span>opening and closing</span> <span>ceremonies</span><span>.</span></span></span></span></p>', 1, 1),
(2, 'Marketing y Comunicación', 'Communication and Marketing', '<p>Un evento de tal&nbsp; magnitud&nbsp; atraer&aacute; no solamente espectadores si no tambi&eacute;n medios de comunicaci&oacute;n locales, nacionales e internacionales que deber&aacute;n coordinar sus &aacute;reas de trabajo en &aacute;reas de prensa,&nbsp; &aacute;rea de fotograf&iacute;a y &aacute;rea mixta</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Apoyar en calidad de redactores de noticias y      eventos deportivos</li>\r\n<li>Apoyar con las posiciones para los fot&oacute;grafos,      reporteros, editores de medios sociales, la galer&iacute;a de los reporteros,      sala de prensa y conferencias asistentes de la habitaci&oacute;n, centro de      servicios y auxiliares de oficina, entre otros.</li>\r\n<li>Brindar servicios de informaci&oacute;n a los      visitantes y ciudadan&iacute;a en general en sitios de informaci&oacute;n dispuestos.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span>An event</span> <span>of this magnitude</span> <span>not only</span> <span>attract</span> <span>viewers</span> <span>but also</span> <span>means</span> <span>of local, national</span> <span>and international</span> <span>communication</span> <span>should coordinate their</span> <span>work areas,</span> <span>press areas</span><span>,</span> <span>area</span> <span>photography and</span> <span>mixed area</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Support</span> <span>as</span> <span>news editors</span> <span>and sporting events</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>To support</span> <span>the positions</span> <span>for photographers,</span> <span>reporters, editors,</span> <span>social media</span><span>,</span> <span>reporters</span> <span>gallery</span><span>, press room</span> <span>and</span> <span>conference</span> <span>room</span> <span>attendants</span><span>, service center</span> <span>and</span> <span>office assistants</span><span>, among others.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Provide</span> <span>information services to</span> <span>visitors</span> <span>and the general public</span> <span>on</span> <span>information sites</span> <span>arranged</span><span>.</span></span></p>', 2, 1),
(3, 'Salud', 'Health', '<p>El &aacute;rea m&eacute;dica ser&aacute; la primera l&iacute;nea de acci&oacute;n en caso de existir alguna urgencia o emergencia, contaremos con peque&ntilde;os grupos de reacci&oacute;n en cada uno de los escenarios deportivos que tendr&aacute;n tareas desde apoyo en el control de dopaje.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Los m&eacute;dicos actuar&aacute;n en caso de emergencias      relacionadas con los atletas y espectadores&nbsp; en las &aacute;reas de      entrenamiento y competici&oacute;n y en la Villa de los Atletas.</li>\r\n<li>Elaborar &nbsp;informes diarios&nbsp;      correspondientes al &aacute;rea m&eacute;dica.</li>\r\n<li>Escolta para toma de muestras.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span><strong></strong></span><span><span><span>The</span> <span>medical area</span> <span>will be the</span> <span>first line of action</span> <span>in</span> <span>case of any</span> <span>emergency or urgent</span><span>,</span> <span>small groups</span> <span>will have</span> <span>reaction</span> <span>in</span> <span>each of the</span> <span>sports venues</span> <span>that</span> <span>will</span> <span>support</span> <span>tasks from</span> <span>doping control</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Doctors</span> <span>should</span> <span>act</span> <span>related to</span> <span>athletes and spectators</span> <span>in the areas of</span> <span>training and competition</span> <span>and the</span> <span>Athletes Village</span> <span>emergencies.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Prepare daily</span> <span>reports for the</span> <span>medical field.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Escort</span> <span>for</span> <span>sampling.</span></span></span></span></p>', 3, 1),
(4, 'Técnica deportiva', 'Sports technique', '<p>Esta &aacute;rea ser&aacute; la encargada de velar y apoyar en el desarrollo de todas las competencias que se llevaran a cabo. Algunas de las tareas que tendr&aacute;n los voluntarios de esta &aacute;rea ser&aacute;n: escoltas deportivos, apoyo en rutas, marcadores, crono metristas, preparaci&oacute;n del campo deportivo y de entrenamiento, entre otros.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Coadyuvar en el desarrollo de las competencias.<strong></strong></li>\r\n<li>Apoyar&nbsp; en pista o a las delegaciones<strong></strong></li>\r\n<li>Distribuir art&iacute;culos deportivos.<strong></strong></li>\r\n<li>Asistir durante las competiciones<strong></strong></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span></span><span><span><span>This area</span> <span>will be responsible</span> <span>for ensuring</span> <span>and</span> <span>support the development</span> <span>of</span> <span>all the skills that</span> <span>will take place</span><span>.</span> <span>Some of the tasks</span> <span>that</span> <span>volunteers</span> <span>will</span> <span>this area</span> <span>be:</span> <span>sports</span> <span>escorts,</span> <span>support</span> <span>routes</span><span>, markers,</span> <span>metristas</span> <span>chrono</span><span>,</span> <span>sports field</span> <span>preparation</span> <span>and</span> <span>training</span><span>, among others.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Assist in</span> <span>the development</span> <span>of skills.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Support</span> <span>on track or</span> <span>delegations</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Distribute</span> <span>sporting goods.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Assist</span> <span>during competitions</span></span></span></span></p>', 4, 1),
(5, 'Transporte', 'Transport', '<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>El transporte de los atletas de ida y vuelta a los escenarios deportivos es fundamental para que la competencia se lleve a cabo, los voluntarios&nbsp; deber&aacute;n coordinar el transporte de cada delegaci&oacute;n, teniendo en cuenta la cantidad de personas y la capacidad de cada uno de los veh&iacute;culos disponibles, bas&aacute;ndose en la tabla de horarios que se le proporcionara.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Coordinar la llegada y salida de los veh&iacute;culos      de transporte</li>\r\n<li>Verificar el cumplimiento de horarios de      llegada y salida del transporte</li>\r\n<li>Verificar las condiciones de seguridad      establecidas de los veh&iacute;culos</li>\r\n<li>Coordinar la necesidad de las delegaciones en      cuanto a transporte</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span></span><span><span><span>Transporting</span> <span>athletes</span> <span>return</span> <span>to</span> <span>sports venues</span> <span>is essential</span> <span>so that competition</span> <span>is done</span><span>, volunteers</span> <span>will</span> <span>coordinate the transportation of</span> <span>each delegation</span><span>,</span> <span>taking into account</span> <span>the number of people</span> <span>and the ability</span> <span>of each</span> <span>vehicle</span> <span>available</span><span>, based on the</span> <span>time table</span> <span>to be provided</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>To coordinate the</span> <span>arrival and departure of</span> <span>transport vehicles</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Verify compliance with</span> <span>arrival and departure</span> <span>times</span> <span>of</span> <span>transport</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Check</span> <span>the safety conditions</span> <span>established</span> <span>vehicles</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Coordinate</span> <span>the need for</span> <span>delegations</span> <span>in transport</span></span></span></span></p>', 5, 1),
(6, 'Hospedaje y alimentación', 'Lodging and meals', '<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>La alimentaci&oacute;n y el hospedaje son dos pilares fundamentales en cuanto al desempe&ntilde;o de un atleta; Los voluntarios de esta &aacute;rea deber&aacute;n encargarse de coordinar la entrega de alimentos en los horarios establecidos, adem&aacute;s de responder ante cualquier contingencia relacionada&nbsp; con el hospedaje.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Solucionar problemas suscitados o necesidades&nbsp; dentro del Hospedaje.</li>\r\n<li>Velar por el buen y correcto servicio y distribuci&oacute;n de alimentos.</li>\r\n<li>Controlar&nbsp; &nbsp;ingreso a los comedores.</li>\r\n<li>Verificar la higiene de las &aacute;reas donde se distribuyen alimentos.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinar la entrega de refrigerio m&oacute;viles a las delegaciones correspondientes</li>\r\n<li>apoyar en los desayunos, almuerzos, cenas y refrigerios facilitando el acceso a los participantes.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span>The</span> <span>food and lodging</span> <span>are</span> <span>two fundamental</span> <span>pillars</span> <span>for performance</span> <span>of an athlete</span><span>;</span> <span>Volunteers</span> <span>in this area</span> <span>should be responsible</span> <span>for coordinating</span> <span>the delivery of food</span> <span>at set times</span><span>, plus</span> <span>respond to any</span> <span>contingency related to</span> <span>hosting.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span><span>&bull;</span> <span>Solving</span> <span>problems encountered</span> <span>or</span> <span>needs within the</span> <span>Accommodation</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Ensure proper</span> <span>and smooth service and</span> <span>food distribution.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Check</span> <span>income</span> <span>eaters</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Check the condition</span> <span>of the areas where</span> <span>food is distributed</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Coordinate the</span> <span>delivery of mobile</span> <span>snack</span> <span>to the corresponding</span> <span>delegations</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>support</span> <span>at breakfast</span><span>, lunch, dinner</span> <span>and snacks</span> <span>facilitating access</span> <span>to participants.</span></span></p>', 6, 1),
(7, 'Escenarios Deportivos', 'Deportive scenary', '<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>os voluntarios de esta &aacute;rea ser&aacute;n encargados del apoyo en cuanto al ingreso del p&uacute;blico a los escenarios, as&iacute; como tambi&eacute;n la evacuaci&oacute;n de los mismos en caso de existir alguna contingencia, tambi&eacute;n se encargaran de la coordinaci&oacute;n del encendido de la luminaria&nbsp; y los almacenes dentro del escenario.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Apoyar al Administrador de Recinto,      supervisi&oacute;n permanente en el cumplimiento de las normas de seguridad en      los Recintos.</li>\r\n<li>Supervisar y vigilar que todos los proveedores      presentes en el recinto, cumplan con las normas de seguridad.</li>\r\n<li>verificar que los extintores est&eacute;n en su      lugar, v&iacute;as de evacuaci&oacute;n y zonas de seguridad est&eacute;n despejadas, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Que las instalaciones t&eacute;cnicas est&eacute;n en su      lugar y dispuestas para la competencia.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span>Volunteers</span> <span>of</span> <span>this area will be</span> <span>responsible for</span> <span>support regarding the</span> <span>admission</span> <span>of the public</span> <span>to the stage</span><span>, as well as</span> <span>the evacuation of</span> <span>the same</span> <span>in</span> <span>case of any</span> <span>contingency</span><span>,</span> <span>is also</span> <span>responsible for coordinating</span> <span>the ignition</span> <span>of the luminaire</span> <span>and stores</span> <span>within the</span> <span>stage.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Support the</span> <span>Manager</span> <span>Complex,</span> <span>permanent</span> <span>monitoring</span> <span>compliance with</span> <span>safety standards</span> <span>Precincts</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>To supervise</span> <span>and monitor</span> <span>all suppliers</span> <span>present</span> <span>on the premises,</span> <span>meet</span> <span>safety standards</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>check</span> <span>that extinguishers</span> <span>are in place</span><span>,</span> <span>escape routes and</span> <span>safety zones</span> <span>are clear</span><span>,</span> <span>etc.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>What</span> <span>technical facilities</span> <span>are in place</span> <span>and ready</span> <span>for competition.</span></span></p>', 7, 1),
(8, 'Tecnologías de información', 'Information technologies', '<ul>\r\n<li>Los voluntarios de esta &aacute;rea apoyaran en cuanto a sistemas de transcripci&oacute;n y registro de tiempos y marcas, gracias a ti podremos conocer los resultados. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Apoyar&nbsp; con el funcionamiento de cuadros      de indicadores de competencia recogiendo y distribuyendo las estad&iacute;sticas      y los resultados</li>\r\n<li>Operar estaciones de radio port&aacute;tiles y      proporcionar apoyo t&eacute;cnico a los servicios de informaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>Operar puntos m&oacute;viles de acreditaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span><span></span><span><span><span>&bull;</span> <span>Volunteers in this</span> <span>area</span> <span>as to</span> <span>support</span> <span>transcription systems</span> <span>and</span> <span>time recording</span> <span>and brands,</span> <span>thanks to you</span> <span>we</span> <span>know the results.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>To support</span> <span>the operation</span> <span>of</span> <span>competition</span> <span>scoreboards</span> <span>collecting and distributing</span> <span>statistics</span> <span>and results</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Operate</span> <span>portable radio</span> <span>stations</span> <span>and provide technical</span> <span>support for</span> <span>information services</span><span>.</span><br /><span>&bull;</span> <span>Trading</span> <span>mobile</span> <span>points of</span> <span>accreditation</span><span>.</span></span></span></span></p>', 8, 1),
(9, 'Servicio a los Comités Olímpicos Nacionales', 'Services NOCS', '<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Los voluntarios estar&aacute;n en contacto directo con las autoridades de los Comit&eacute;s Ol&iacute;mpicos Nacionales y los Jefes de misi&oacute;n de cada uno de los 14 pa&iacute;ses que participaran en los juegos, estos voluntarios deber&aacute;n tendr&aacute;n la capacidad de resolver cualquier contingencia que pueda suceder.</p>\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Acompa&ntilde;aran a los jefes de misi&oacute;n y ejecutivos&nbsp; de ODESUR durante todos los d&iacute;as, solucionando inquietudes o posibles problemas que se vayan a presentar en el transcurso de los juegos.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span><span><span><span>Volunteers will be</span> <span>in direct contact with</span> <span>the authorities of the</span> <span>National Olympic Committees and</span> <span>the heads of</span> <span>mission</span> <span>of</span> <span>each of the</span> <span>14</span> <span>countries participating in</span> <span>the games,</span> <span>these</span> <span>volunteers should</span> <span>have the ability to</span> <span>resolve any</span> <span>contingency that may</span> <span>happen.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span><span><span>A<span>ccompany</span> <span>heads of mission</span> <span>and</span> <span>executives</span> <span>ODESUR</span> <span>every day</span><span>, solving</span> <span>potential</span> <span>concerns or</span> <span>problems</span> <span>that will be</span> <span>present</span> <span>during</span> <span>the games.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 9, 1),
(10, 'Villa Suramericana', 'Villa Suramericana', '', '', 10, 0),
